Beaker in a box

A stash of Ansible playbooks and Vagrant that allow you to install and configure a complete
working Beaker environment, including three virtual guests to act as test systems.

Requirements
  - Ansible
  - Host capable of running libvirt
  - Vagrant

Set up libvirt Network on the host
  - make sure you can SSH to localhost without password
  - run `ansible-playbook -i hosts site.yml -K`
    This command will create a libvirt network.
